+# Changelog 2026-06-06
+
+- Implemented dependency-free basket pricing with explicit input validation.
+- Chose per-line category discount rounding before tax so subtotal, tax, and shipping follow the pricing contract exactly.
diff --git a/src/priceBasket.mjs b/src/priceBasket.mjs
